== xkbcomp at X startup ==
=== Issue Description ===
xkbcomp at X startup is unnecessary performance penalty. Possible alternatives:
 1. Rewriting xkbcomp to make it more effecient (for example, by caching the configuration)
 2. Using shared library directly from X server. That library would also be used by setxkbmap.
=== Status/Owner ===
=== Bug(s) ===
[[https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=15540|#15540]]
== XKM format should be deprecated ==
=== Issue Description ===
XKM as a binary format has some serious issues:
 1. Not readable
 2. Some information is not presentable (see [[https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=4927|#4927]])
 3. ''TBC'' (Daniel, feel free to express all your hatred here;)
Textual XKB format should be the only format of the persistant configuration data used by XKB.
=== Status/Owner ===
=== Bug(s) ===
