== xkbcomp needs :all syntax for rules ==
=== Issue Description ===
The following functionality is needed in xkbcomp:
If some XKB option is using some symbols in group 1, they should be propagated
to all groups present in the configuration. Something like

! option = symbols

og:abc = symfile(v):all

// equal to og:abc = symfile(v):1 + symfile(v):2 + ... till the last group
=== Status/Owner ===
