== setxkbmap is unable to explain the rules it applied  ==
=== Issue Description ===
Sometimes setxkbmap makes non-trivial decisions regarding the way it applies
the rules. Even using dozen of -v options does not help. What would be useful
to have is some way to see the list of the rules applied to the input
components (with references to line numbers in the rules file perhaps).
